Use Your Time Wisely

Some airports even have shoppings malls and or centres. But I can use that time to get all caught up on flight safety. I mean I have the two hours I have from getting there early. Like hand out completion certificates, with passports and or with arriving and taking the training at the airport like you have the time. Dont make me have to listen to you on the plane. text:
Matthew 7:5 James 2:20  
Self Love. To Self Acceptance. To Self Confidence. 

 But First My Speck.  
Song Inspo Ghost by Justin Bieber.   Don’t Settle for the Ghost of Yourself.   You won’t win that way in the long run.   You’ll ask for Confidence. To feel Holy.  Because you’ll be Lonely. With only your  Ghost to keep you Company. Sorry. 
 It’s That People love Your Looks. 
And Or Sense Of Self Expression. And or Self Acceptance. And As such  Self Confidence. And or just Self Love. 

Its the year times for the alternative.

Matthew 7:5 James 2:20
I can respect it. Its the year times for the alternative.
Post The Weeknd Dreads. We've gone through so many changes that right now. High fashion basic fashion. Its all already been done. Either youre in nudes, walking around looking homeless and or letting your weird flag fly and showing your own creativity, is what it often times feels like right now. There is like no societal pressure. It really is like be who you really and truly are. 

Show your own sense of self. And or feed into your very own outlets of self expression. And he's doing that. Its not hidden behind the va va room. Its his sense of expression its different. Its unique. And its him. He allows himself to be him. To be different in a world that oftentimes can feel like it forces you to fit into a mould he shows himself. Allow himself to create his own mould. And or walk out and go his own way.   He beats to the beat of his own drum with his look. Individuality. Of course people want that. Even Billie Eilish admitted that she's always wanted to dress up when she did the whole Desperate Housewives Meets Cinderella Outfit at the Met Gala. And he's doing it. What so many are really actually afraid to do. Showing himself. His creative self. His sense of self expression. 

His individuality. He's not letting his fears determine his fate. Even if people laugh and or mock you. Soon they will ask if you are hiring. And or how? Are you not scared and or afraid of what others may think when you dress different?   Act Different? Just accept yourself. Just allow yourself to be yourself? I dont know what his answer is but he doesnt let that stop him. He expresses himself. In a world where so many people talk and dream. He's out there doing and living by his dreams in his own reality. 

He's not hiding his light. He allows himself to be himself. And that is is hot as fxxk. So yeah women want him for his looks but also for a whole lot more a whole lot deeper of what it actually represents. "Not letting your fears determine your fates" -- Victoria's Tattoo. And "If you walk with the wise then maybe you too will be wise" -- tHB. And maybe that courage will rub off on you. 

Especially in a world where so many women bodies are so often like almost feeling fully regulated and Attacked for literally anything and almost anything that they do. ITs like but guys wont like you if... its like this guy is doing him. And thats what Im trying to do. 

So if youre walking with someoen who is going there own way then maybe you will be okay with going your own way too. Its the heart. Its the light. Its the fulfilment. He has it within him this world time. 

Lil Mama Lip Gloss Inspo. Popping. Yeah I believe. You can start small. But slowly and yet surely you too will be more and more comfortable with being comfortable within your own skin. 

And or (just) comfortable being and or also expressing yourself. Within your various outlets for self expressions!!!! Just take your time with you. You are your best investment. Youre best project. Project Song Inspo Chase McDaniels. Best, X. Inn Jesus Name, Amen.
